🚨Quick story time 🚨
The other day my friends @shaunieestylez & @kidheat called me and told me we were going out! Truthfully I wasn’t in the place to even WANT to go out, but when your friends ask… I don’t have many friends as it is lol so I went. We ended up at @omnianightclub to go watch @steveaoki Now when we got there, it was SOOOOOO packed we could barely even get to the back to see his head (view from the first video) Then suddenly I see @chris_cbv_bermudez working. I just go to say what’s up but he looked out for our little group and told us he could get us closer to the stage so we could see Steve better. I immediately jumped at the opportunity and we went (view from other videos) @steveaoki was truly Inspiring! I remember being a kid and watching his story of how he became a DJ. (If you guys haven’t heard the story you definitely should check it out) but me Being from Vegas Steve was always around and playing at the clubs so getting to meet him and be next to him was crazy for me. I remember when I first got there, seeing Steve on stage and seeing all those people and I thought to myself. “This will be You one day” I visualized it, I saw it so vividly, standing in the exact same spot @steveaoki was standing. Then… What happened next was like some 💩 straight out of a movie. See my next post to see what I’m talking about 👀

Then this happened…
